I'd be happier to ditch the fork, attributions and all.

With this I can just
sed 's,^# HELPDIR should be.*,: ${HELPDIR:=/usr/share/zsh/help},;s,:-more,:-/usr/bin/pager,' Functions/Misc/run-help

Better ideas are welcome.

